Package: clickStories
Title: Generate Quarto Reveal.js Click-Through Data Stories
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Encoding: UTF-8
Authors@R: 
    person("Madoc Alder", "Marshall", , "mmarshall@astho.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           )
Description: This package allows you to quickly create compelling click-through data stories using a variety of viz formats, from embedded HTML code, to local images. It generates a Quarto RevealJS document and necessary file directory and, if needed, can generate a self containeed html doc version of the click-through.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
